attachments.text: Quick tip - to simulate phone vibration in a Framer prototype, you can use the WebAudio api to emit a low frequency pulse. At least on my MacBook I can feel an appropriate amount of haptic feedback....

text: That video loop is great. I haven't dug into Framer yet, still need to. Have you used it yourself Gaston?
Used a little bit of Framer before but not this particular demo.
This one is really cool b/c I've been playing with WebAudio lately and it's nice to see it being used in this way.
